  "detailed_description": "Explore an isolated space station to uncover a dark secret behind the station's true purpose.<br>Search for clues in a 1st person perspective. Question your crewmates. Research your loss of memory. Discover what happened to the missing Overseers. <br>This experimental interactive short story will keep you guessing until the very end!<br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Immersive First Person perspective.<br></li><li>Fully vocalized by talented actors.<br></li><li>Experimental Interactive sci-fi thriller.<br></li><li>Adapted from the Short Story by Catalina Leon.</li></ul>",
